{"title":"女兵——有感于一幅新闻摄影","authors":["苏正新"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":8,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"女兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——有感于一幅新闻摄影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏正新"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伫立于暴雨后的大街上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伫立于齐胸深的洪水中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手拉着手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽起一排和平的栏杆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让男女老幼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从这儿安然穿行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像挺立于水上的荷苞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜甜地笑着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"构成一道动人的风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而凶猛的洪水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随时可能吞噬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她们年轻美丽的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个都是花季般的年龄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假若在家里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大约还会撒娇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碰上下大雨的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会像叽喳的小鸟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躲进大人们的怀抱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪水里的女兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢无畏的女兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可亲可敬的女兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让人不禁想起——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座巨大的熔炉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——绿色军营"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}